cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on the use of recurrent neural networks for modeling mechanical systems and using them for model-based Reinforcement Learning. This falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also proposes an adaptive Model Predictive Controller scheme, which involves optimization and learning, making it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of neural networks for modeling and control also falls under robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper proposes a new type of recurrent neural network, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
